              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">度厄真符</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/900dec327166a00218479cf8616072fc_6788285193357997137.png",
                "id": "talent42454",
                "key": "仙法 · 救苦度厄",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "仙法 · 救苦度厄"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召唤物在场时，七七使用「普通攻击」后：</span>治疗受伤最多的我方角色1点；每回合1次：再治疗我方出战角色1点。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5627087868365334505.png",
                "id": "talent17986",
                "key": "寒病鬼差",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/971b05c02dd20b662457e953c3c1ce93_5637562911296817301.png",
                "title": "寒病鬼差"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6816009295859703877.png",
                "id": "talent1289",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">度厄真符</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色使用技能后：</span>如果该角色生命值未满，则治疗该角色2点。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6082419919068804739.png",
